.SH CONFIGURATION
.PP
\f[B]atspkg\f[] is configured with Dhall, in an atspkg.dhall file.
\f[B]atspkg\f[] can be configured to produce binary targets (possibly
linked against Haskell libraries), as well as plain C targets.
